name: I feel something move inside...
description:
Returning to the origin #002

Returning to the origin, this is a series of works where the exploration starts from the idea of making an image disappear, a memory. From the concrete will be sought to reach the undefined, the imprecise, something more abstract. As when we have an idea and we have not yet been able to translate it into something real and only a mental representation remains, a question mark in our head, with a more free form and movement. That's why the name, returning to the origin. Everything in our head is form and movement. 

By Lo-collage.
